Hi <%= @recipient.name %>,

<% if @cancelled_by == 'customer' %>
The customer <%= @appointment.customer.name %> has cancelled their appointment with you.
<% else %>
Unfortunately, <%= @appointment.stylist.name %> has cancelled your upcoming appointment.
<% end %>

Appointment Details:
  Service:    <%= @appointment.selected_service %>
  Date & Time: <%= @appointment.time.strftime('%A, %B %-d at %-I:%M %p') %>
<% if @appointment.location.present? %>  Location:   <%= @appointment.location_display %>
<% end %><% if @appointment.cancellation_reason.present? %>  Reason:     <%= @appointment.cancellation_reason %>
<% end %>
<% if @recipient_role == 'customer' && @refund_issued %>
REFUND ISSUED: Your deposit of <%= number_to_currency(@appointment.payment_amount.to_f * 0.5) %> will be returned within 5-10 business days.
<% elsif @recipient_role == 'customer' && @appointment.payment_status == 'deposit_kept' %>
NO REFUND: This cancellation was made within 24 hours of your appointment. Your deposit has been kept per our cancellation policy.
<% end %>
If you have questions, contact us through the ChairHop app.

The ChairHop Team
